window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's civil war! </p> <p>For years, Earth's heroes fought united. They faced alien armies in war. They defended Earth as friends. As a fellowship. </p> <p>Now they break apart. </p> <p>Lailani de la Rosa, heroine of the Alien Wars, aligns herself with a new enemy. She rises to lead the scummers, a breed of human-alien hybrids. </p> <p>Earth's remaining heroes, led by President Einav Ben-Ari, must face her in war. </p> <p>Lailani knows all of Earth's secrets. She is smarter and stronger than any alien. She is the greatest threat humanity has ever faced. </p> <p>United, we've stood against many foes. Divided, will we fall?</p>"; 
